                              "code": "\tdataset \u003d system.dataset.toPyDataSet(value)\n\tdatalist \u003d []\n\tparams \u003d {\u0027value\u0027:\u0027All\u0027,\u0027label\u0027:\u0027Select All\u0027}\n\tdatalist.append(params)\n\tfor data in dataset:\n\t\tparams \u003d {\u0027value\u0027:data[\u0027value\u0027],\u0027label\u0027:data[\u0027label\u0027]}\n\t\tdatalist.append(params)\n\treturn datalist",
